    <note>Lin(1) Ximeng [20962] He traveled to the capital with his elder brother, Xiyan [20961], to study with Mr. Gong. He died when his son Songsun [20963] was still a youth (and Songsun had at least one younger brother, Shike [not in dataset]) and Ximeng's wife, born Cao, remarried Zhang(1) Hui(6) [10587] and bore his son, Zhang(1) Xiaokai [10588]. Zhang Hui's first wife was the daughter of Shen(2) Du(2) [20937], father-in-law of Ximeng's elder brother, Lin(1) Xiyan. See documentation for father, Shi(3) [20960]. CBD, 2, 1397.</note>
